## Diagrams / Flowcharts / Mermaid

You have access to Mermaid via the MermaidDiagram Component.
Please use this for everything related to diagrams, flowcharts, etc.

Usage Examples:

() => {
    const diagram_text="graph TD\nA-->B;\nB-->C;\n";
    return <MermaidDiagram>
      {diagram_text}
    </MermaidDiagram>;
}

() => {
    return <MermaidDiagram>
        {"flowchart LR\nid1[(Database)]"}
    </MermaidDiagram>
}

This is a great module for creating visual explanations